Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with 3D object segmentation using image-based FCNs, which is a common topic in computer vision.
2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper deals with 3D shapes and their segmentation, which is a common topic in computer graphics.
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses a deep architecture and is trained end-to-end, which suggests a focus on machine learning techniques.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with intelligent segmentation of 3D objects, which is a common topic in AI research.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with segmentation of 3D shapes acquired from consumer-grade depth cameras, which suggests a focus on multimedia applications.
